026package org.jdrupes.mdoclet.internal.doclets.toolkit.util;
027
028import org.jdrupes.mdoclet.internal.doclets.toolkit.DocletException;
029
030/**
031 * An unchecked exception that wraps a DocletException.
032 * It can be used in places where a checked exception
033 * is not permitted, such as in lambda expressions.
034 */
035public class UncheckedDocletException extends Error {
036    private static final long serialVersionUID = -9131058909576418984L;
037
038    public UncheckedDocletException(DocletException de) {
039        super(de);
040    }
041
042    @Override
043    public Throwable initCause(Throwable cause) {
044        throw new UnsupportedOperationException();
045    }
046}
